---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Karongi (Kibuye) - Lake Kivu's Peninsula Paradise">
  <Header />
  
  <div style="padding-top: 120px;" class="s">
    <div class="s-narrow" style="margin: 0 auto;">
      <span class="s-label">Lake Kivu</span>
      <h1 class="s-heading">Karongi<br><em>The Peninsula Paradise</em></h1>
      <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <img src="/images/kigali_modern_life_1763983567881.png" alt="Karongi peninsula on Lake Kivu" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;">
      </div>
      <div class="s-body" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <p>Karongi (formerly Kibuye) is arguably the most beautiful town on Lake Kivu, perched on a series of peninsulas surrounded by rolling green hills. Its relaxed atmosphere and stunning lake views make it a favorite among travelers seeking tranquility.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Top Experiences</h3>
        <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; list-style-position: inside;">
          <li>🏝️ Napoleon Island — boat trip to bat-filled caves and picnic spots</li>
          <li>💧 Peace Island — tranquil retreat with walking trails</li>
          <li>🚤 Morning Boat Tours — explore the lake's many inlets</li>
          <li>🕯️ Bisesero Memorial — moving genocide memorial site</li>
          <li>🏞️ Lake Kivu Loop — scenic walking and cycling trails</li>
          <li>🏨 Bethany House — historic missionary guesthouse with lake views</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Activities</h3>
        <p>Kayaking, swimming, and hiking are popular here. The hills around Karongi offer spectacular viewpoints overlooking the lake's countless islands. Many visitors rent bikes to explore the shoreline villages and coffee farms.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box" style="background: var(--bg2); padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);">
          <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Hidden Gem</h4>
          <p>Karongi is less developed than Gisenyi, offering a more authentic and peaceful lake experience. It's the perfect midpoint stop on the classic Rwanda circuit between Nyungwe Forest and Musanze.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>